snippet: A Democratic state senator, Joe Baca, defeated a Republican businessman today in an election to replace the late Representative George E. Brown Jr., a Democratic lawmaker who died in July....
lead_paragraph: A Democratic state senator, Joe Baca, defeated a Republican businessman today in an election to replace the late Representative George E. Brown Jr., a Democratic lawmaker who died in July.
abstract: Democratic state senator Joe Baca defeats Elia Pirozzi, Republican businessman, in election in California to replace state Repr George E Brown Jr, Democratic lawmaker who died in July (S)
